      "clean_text": "23.\tThe s 5 exception to state immunity applies to claims for personal injury, including psychiatric injury. It is not limited to cases in which personal injury is a ‘direct consequence’ of the conduct complained of: Federal Republic of Nigeria v Ogbonna [2012] 1 WLR 139, [6(5)] and [13], per Underhill J (as he then was)."
